# journaling stack — commit the mirrored SOURCE only (compose.yaml, .env.example, the
# n8n *.workflow.json, templates/, scripts/, openwebui/). NEVER the live bind-mount
# state or secrets: memos/ holds the sqlite DB + uploads, whisper-cache/ the HF models,
# n8n/ (except the workflow JSONs) holds the n8n sqlite + the ENCRYPTION KEY, and .env
# carries the Memos PAT. restic backs the live copies up on the mini; the repo carries
# source only (anti-drift — see CLAUDE.md file-ownership map).
.env
memos/
whisper-cache/
n8n/*
!n8n/*.workflow.json
# portable exports produced by scripts/export-journal.sh
journal-export-*.json
exports/
